book_contents.elemental_magic.page1: Elemental Magic is a type of Magic that consists of Magic many know around them, the well known ones are: §cFire§r, §9Water§r, §bIce§r, §2Nature§r, §8Earth§r, §fWind§r, §4Magma§r, §3Souls§r, and many more.
book_contents.elemental_magic.page2: Elemental Magic can be different in what World and Reality you come from, whether your from the Reality or Fantasy, it doesn't matter as long as there is Proof that magic exists in your World.
book_contents.elemental_magic.page3: If your world is Reality or a world from Fantasy but no Magic, then alternatively this book can at least give you ideas for your own entertainment or information.
